doctors.biography:
Dr. Anila Smajlaj, DMD

Dr. Anila graduated with honors from thefrom the Faculty of Dentistry at Our Lady ofat Our Lady of Good Counsel University in 2011in 2011 .

She completed a Master's Degree in Prosthodontics and Gnathology , specializing in complex restorative cases, full mouth rehabilitation , and implant prosthetics .

Dr. Anila practices all aspects of general dentistry for both adults and children , with a primary focus on prosthodontics and endodontics .for both adults and children , with a primary focus on prosthodontics and endodontics .

She stays continuously updated on the latest dental techniques through ongoing continuing education courses .on the latest dental techniques through ongoing continuing education courses .

Dr. Anila provides comprehensive cosmetic dental services , including:

Veneers

All-ceramic restorations

Full mouth reconstructions

Implant-supported prostheses

Aesthetic rehabilitations
